<h1 id="documentation-for-shopify">Documentation for Shopify</h1>

<p>ShopRunBack provides an official addon for Shopify users.</p>

<p>You can connect your shop to ShopRunBack by visiting this link: <a href="https://shopify.shoprunback.com">https://shopify.shoprunback.com</a>.</p>

<p>Once there, enter the URL of your own shop and accepts all the requested rights of the addon.</p>

<p>Then, you will be redirected to the ShopRunBack Dashboard and invited to create your account and company if not already done.</p>

<p>Your shop is now connected to ShopRunBack. You just have to add the return link on your order details page to redirect your customer to the return process.</p>

<p>If you have any question, please send an email to: tech_at_shoprunback.com</p>
